text: Atalaya natalensis, also called Natal wing-nut, is a species of plant in the family Sapindaceae. It is endemic to the Cape Provinces and KwaZulu-Natal in South Africa. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== Category:Flora of the Cape Provinces Category:Flora of KwaZulu-Natal natalensis Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
